--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TO SETUP AFTER YOU CLONE THIS PROJECT:
run command: composer install
run command: php sb setup --host=http://sb.local.com --dbuser=root --dbname=starbug --dbprefix=sb_
run command: composer dump-autoload

NOTE: Setup variables above are defaults. You can also edit them afterwards in var/etc/di.php

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHEN PULLING NEW CODE:
run command: composer migrate

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHEN YOU FIRST CREATE A PROJECT, INSTALL AND COMMIT THE LIBRARIES:
run command: bower install
run command: git add libraries
run command: git commit -am "libraries"
run command: git push

